<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038117" n="1"/> 
<opener><salute>
  <lb/>Viro Reverendo et Clarissimo
  <lb/><abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119112450">Jacobo Hermanno</rs> 
  <lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr>
  <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119166895">Nicolaus Bernoull<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></rs>.</salute></opener>
  <p><lb/>Co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>od<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> se mihi jam <add>pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>bente</add> ad Te scribendi occasion<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Adgnato
    <lb/>meo</rs>, iniquum fore existimavi si eum in <add><rs type="place" key="place_KON-italie">Italicas</rs></add> abeuntem oras nullis ad te literis comita<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rer; debito itaque meo ut satisfaciam, paucis his Te interpellare aggredior. Primum
    <lb/>quidem Tibi gratias ago non leves pro benigno Tuo in me animo, quem literis ad <abbr>Cl.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="">Patruum
    <lb/>meum</rs> testatus es, dum significasti te admodum cupere, ut Tibi in statione Tua <rs type="place">Patavina</rs>
    <lb/>aliquando succederem; ex quo cum <add>l<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tus</add> perspiciam, Te non minus de co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>odis meis promovendis
    <lb/>cogitare quam <rs type="person">Patruum</rs> meum, qui ignorante me hac de re ad Te scripsit, utrique
    <lb/>vestrum <unclear>cum</unclear><!-- ToDo: kontrollieren. In der Spiesstranskription stand "hoc". --> nomine <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quali jure su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>opere me esse obligatum profiteor; Interim <add>ver<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice></add> cum provin<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ci<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> huic tam pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>clare, ut <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Te fit, exornand<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> omnino non par sim, <add>vehementer opto</add>, ut
    <lb/><rs type="organisation">Academi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> hujus illustris decus esse diu pergas, donec Te fam<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> indies crescentis cele<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>britas in eum tandem locum perducat, ubi magis ex voto eruditionem Tuam cum
    <lb/><add>aliis</add> co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>unicare et meritis tuis eam, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> i<unclear>st</unclear>is<!-- ToDo: kontrollieren, es könnte auch "ipsis" sein. --> debetur, laudem astruere queas<add>.</add>
    <lb/><rs type="letters">Literas</rs> quas ante annum circiter <rs type="person">Patrui</rs> mei <rs type="letters">literis</rs> inclusas ad Te misi, credo Te accepisse.
    <lb/><add>Paulo post id tempus, quo eas ad Te dedi</add> iter <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2661552">Bernam</rs>, dehinc <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2660646">Genevam</rs>, et inde <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2988507">Lutetiam</rs> suscepi, ubi qua m<unclear reason="lost">e</unclear>
    <lb/>benevolentia <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119062372">Varignonius</rs> et reliqu<add>i fere omnes</add> Academic<add>i</add> excep<unclear reason="lost">e</unclear><pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rint, vix dicere possum; liber aditus mihi<note type="editorial">Wortumstellung.</note> ut et <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-120379260">Scheuchzero</rs> juniori, qui sub idem fere tem<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>pus ex <rs type="place" key="place_VER-belgie">Belgio</rs> <rs type="place" key="place_VER-belgie">Parisios</rs> venerat, ad comitia <rs type="organisation">Academi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Regi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> et <add>sedes</add> inter ipsos Academicos
    <lb/>concessa fu<unclear>i</unclear>t. Discessum <add>nostrum</add> plures <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>gre tulerunt, inprimis <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119062372">Varignonius</rs>, qui ut per hyemem
    <lb/>maneremus nobis omnib<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> modis persuadere conat<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> est. Litem illam de spatiis plusquam
    <lb/>infinitis <add>de qua tibi scripsi</add> nil nisi Logomachiam esse ex ipso <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119062372">Varignonio</rs> intellexi, dari enim varios infinito<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rum gradus confitetur, et solum negat fractionem, cujus denominator est negativus, exprimere
    <lb/>rationem plusquam infinite magnam, adeo<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118771167">Wallisium</rs> male conclusisse asserit spatia
    <lb/>illa hyperbolica ad parallegra<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>a inscripta habere rationem plusquam infinitam, <add>exinde</add>
    <lb/>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice>d illorum ratio sit ut numeri positivi ad numerum negativum; in quo etiam ego
    <lb/>ipsi potius assentior quam <abbr>P.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118937669">Grando</rs> qu<add>i</add> adeo frustraneam collocavit operam, si id
    <lb/>tantum pro scopo habuit, ut <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119062372">Varignonium</rs> refutaret. Injurius etiam est in <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119062372">Varignoni<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs>
    <lb/>dum <abbr>pag.</abbr> <space/><!-- Hier steht eine Lücke, in der die Seitenzahl einzufügen war. ToDo: Eventuell die korrekte Seitenzahl aufgrund der Textstelle ergänzen. --> asserit, illum male facere angulum contactus angulo ad centrum circuli
    <pb facs="1038118" n="2"/>
    <lb/>osculatoris <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualem, cum hic illius dupl<unclear>u</unclear>s sit, adeo<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> illum male determinasse longitu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dinem radii osculi, et quantitatem virium centralium, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quam<!-- ToDo: kontrollieren ob quae quam oder quaequam. --> bene dicta sint,
    <lb/>ipse judicabis. <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117601020">Remondus de Montmort</rs>, qui specimen illud de <rs type="keyword">Ludis Fortun<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> edidit, per <rs type="letters">literas</rs>
    <lb/>ad <rs type="person">Patruum</rs> petiit, ut sibi Defuncti <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509950">Patrui</rs> mei Tractatus Manuscript<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_WPXENY2H">de Arte Con<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>jectandi</rs> co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>ittere<choice><orig><g ref="#tur">&#xf199;</g></orig><reg>tur</reg></choice>, pollicitus se illum propriis sumtibus editurum; proposui hoc <rs type="person">Adgnato</rs>
    <lb/>meo, sed ille pro sua et totius domus su<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <add>stolida</add> in
    <lb/><rs type="person">Patruum</rs> <add>nostr<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></add> et me diffidentia suspectum habet quicquid <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> nobis proficiscitur,
    <lb/>metuens ne quis inventa <rs type="person">Patris</rs> sui sibi arroget; Tecum tamen hac
    <lb/>de causa se consilia initurum respondit, quocirca si tibi <rs type="biblio">tractatum</rs> hunc, ut vide<choice><orig><g ref="#tur">&#xf199;</g></orig><reg>tur</reg></choice>,
    <lb/>co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>ittet, cura qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>so, ut mox prodeat, ne alii, qui interea similia inveniunt, invento<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rum gloriam <foreign xml:lang="grc">τώ <!-- ToDo kontrollieren ob auf dem Omega noch ein Spiritus steht. -->μακαρίτη</foreign><note type="editorial">"dem Verstorbenen, Seligen".</note> debitam pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ripiant. De lite <abbr>D.</abbr> <abbr>Prof.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-116082356">Battierio</rs> ob defens<unclear><choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></unclear>
    <lb/>in <rs type="biblio">Dissertatione de Mundo Copernican<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> Systema</rs> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> quibusdam Theologis <add>syllabizantib<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> et</add> <hi rend="u"><rs type="persons" key="pers_DE-588-118607308 pers_DE-588-120379260">fratrum
      <lb/>Tigurinorum</rs></hi> exemplum pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tendentibus mota forte ex <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patruo</rs> audies. Novi pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terea
    <lb/>nil scio. </p><closer>Vale et novo, quem mox ingrediemur, anno multisque sequentib<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> feliciter vive.
  <dateline><lb/><rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2661604">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <abbr>d.</abbr> <date when="1710-12-27">27. xbris 1710</date>.</dateline></closer>
